In Home Create New Folder inside HOME: data
Inside that folder create new folder: db

Now, we need to run mongodb server

In terminal, type : mongod --dbpath=data/db -> mongod -> mongo (Server Started) 

After that open the API folder and start terminal

Com 1 : npm start (it might show error) 
	If error shown: Open package.json file and remove mon from nodemon.


